query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `marketBenchmarks` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `sector` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `position` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `region` varchar(100) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Brasil',
  `avgPerformanceScore` int,
  `avgEngagementScore` int,
  `avgTurnoverRate` int,
  `avgTenureYears` int,
  `avgSalary` int,
  `medianSalary` int,
  `avgDiscD` int,
  `avgDiscI` int,
  `avgDiscS` int,
  `avgDiscC` int,
  `avgOpenness` int,
  `avgConscientiousness` int,
  `avgExtraversion` int,
  `avgAgreeableness` int,
  `avgNeuroticism` int,
  `sampleSize` int,
  `dataSource` varchar(255),
  `year` int NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `marketBenchmarks_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
